## Task Description

Predict the species and color of an iris flower based on its petal and sepal dimensions. Petal and sepal dimensions are provided in centimeters. Also, the color of the iris flower will be considered in the prediction. The assistant should consider both petal and sepal dimensions, as well as the color of the iris flower, to determine the species and color. The assistant should use a strategy that takes into account the ranges of petal and sepal dimensions for each species, and the color patterns for each species.

